{"tid":1657920,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【市道不景氣】楊明3間燉湯店蝕錢 盼社會局勢回復平靜","createTime":"2019-10-16T10:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T15:54:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e88d6eb154d44e8149d140097cf940194fcd4f06","tid":1657920,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:04:32.000Z","msg":"楊明和高海寧今日出席《Gi味俱全》記者會。楊明其中一間燉湯店近日捲入反修例風波，事後他發出鄭重聲明。提到市場不景氣，楊明坦言3間燉湯店生意的總和正蝕錢中：「現時市場氣氛都是這樣，希望局勢會快點回復平靜，過回平常生活。（生意如何？）都要蝕，3間店總和都要蝕，不打緊，香港人都捱緊頂住，有時我都落舖頭幫手。」楊明稱暫未想到出動優惠救亡生意，「因為舖頭的食品已好低價，目前是要做好食材管理」。慶幸的是，荔枝角分店獲業主減舖租20%，其他店舖也嘗試爭取減租，希望大眾一起共渡時艱。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WLc8E4y4GJ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWLc8E4y4GJ8&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVj4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=360ca0fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WLc8E4y4GJ8</a>"},{"pid":"9f2378d9d2698177a1568e80303e9df1820a85e1","tid":1657920,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:04:50.000Z","msg":"【再次有圖有真相】令街坊知道1020遊行嘅最佳方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657842</a>"},{"pid":"3c9eb797d2ba5cf3ae3d0093b78ffbce924060ce","tid":1657920,"uid":4574,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"幫屍冥 勤力啲奶閪啦<br />\n牛油狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712dbca151427cd5002e3cf5f8d0ceb881b143a9","tid":1657920,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"唔撚柒會食 <br />\n1020見"},{"pid":"3745a327a858363bbac3bc922155c941b0d1caef","tid":1657920,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c9eb797d2ba5cf3ae3d0093b78ffbce924060ce","tid":1657920,"uid":4574,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10:07:15.000Z","msg":"幫屍冥 勤力啲奶閪啦<br />\n牛油狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" c